name: ET de Varginha com AVC no Domingão do CUSAO
name_original: ET de Varginha com AVC no Domingão do CUSAO
description:
ET DE VARGINHA IS INVITED BY CUSAO TO HIS AUDITORIUM PROGRAM TO DO "SE VIRA NOS 40" TO SHOW HIS ABILITIES WITH DILDOS, BUT ACCIDENTALY ENDS UP THROWING CUSAO IN A REMOTE CONTROL BARBECUE. THIS LEAVES THE PRESENTERS OF OTHER AUDITORIUM PROGRAMS VERY PISSED, SENDING THEIR MINIONS TO FINISH OFF ET DE VARGINHA, WITH ENEMIES LIKE XAPORITOS
GENRE: HACK N SLASH WITH DARK SOULS ELEMENTS LIKE ROLLING
